	The JiraSyncConfigDialog shall populate the server dropdown from SettingsManager.get_jira_servers() and pre-select the previously saved sync server from SettingsManager.get_jira_sync_server().	functional requirement	1.4.2	PO-JIRA-026.0	Not relevant	approved	aligned
