	When "Full resync" is selected from the Sync from Jira dropdown, the sync engine shall be invoked with force_full_resync=True, bypassing the last-sync timestamp and re-fetching all issues matching the configured filter regardless of any incremental mode setting.	functional requirement	2.2.7	PO-J2P-049.0	Not relevant	approved	aligned
